    <item>
      <title>汽车制造业落后于美国和中国，日本专注于智能汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/japan-focuses-on-smart-cars-as-automakers-fall-behind-us-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本正在加大力度推动汽车制造商开发可通过云技术管理的智能汽车，而在这一领域日本汽车制造商已经落后于中国和美国的竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/japan-focuses-on-smart-cars-as-automakers-fall-behind-us-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 02:58:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究称中国电动汽车制造商 15 年来获得 2,310 亿美元援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/china-s-ev-makers-got-231-billion-in-aid-over-last-15-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究显示，尽管每辆车的补贴金额有所下降，但中国电动汽车行业从 2009 年到去年底仍获得了至少 2,310 亿美元的政府补贴和援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/china-s-ev-makers-got-231-billion-in-aid-over-last-15-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 01:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
